---
title: Cheesy Lava Pork Patties & Chargrilled Capsicum Relish with Kūmara Fries & Tomato Salad
description: It’s all hands on deck, this recipe is designed to be cooked by grown-ups and kids together! Get ready for a cheesy
explosion! These stuffed pork patties are packed with melty goodness, paired with tangy chargrilled capsicum relish, crispy kūmara fries, and a fresh tomato salad. It’s a flavour-packed feast that’ll have your taste buds doing a happy dance!
This recipe is under 650kcal per serving and under 40g carbohydrates per serving.
